      WE WILL RECURSE AS SOON AS WE COME ACROSS THE REFERENCE TO THE
      TYPE PARAMETER AS BEING A TYPE ARGUMENT, WHICH WILL MAKE US LOOK UP THE BOUND,
      AND IN TURN WE WILL COME BACK HERE AGAIN TO LOOK UP THE BOUND AGAIN.
      SO WE NEED A WAY TO BREAK THE LOOP IN A WAY THAT STILL ALLOWS THE SPAN
      DO BE WELL FORMED AND READY TO USE IN CONTEXT (USE METHODS OF ITS BOUND)

      MAYBE IN PRACTICE THIS WILL TURN OUT TO NEED A SIMILAR SOLUTION TO HOW
